c: 24
v: 37
t: "Achalume, ŵangakukwapaga chipaka kusuma ni kusumisya (malonda) chakulechela kunkumbuchila Allah (muntima ni palulimi), ni kwimika Swala mwakolosya nambo soni kutola Zaka, akasalijogopaga Lisiku lyajichigalaukagalauka mitima mulyalakwelyo ni meso, (ligongo lyakogoya nnope kwa ipotesi yakwe)"